4:
The hell'd you say to me? You got a
death wish or something?!
5:
Bring it on! It's about time somebody
put you in your place!
8: Don't tell me that's who I think it is...
12:
You're gonna regret picking a fight
with me, punk!
15:
Be grateful I bothered giving you a
warning, newbie!
19: Aaaahh! Please don't egg her on!
26:
You're in public. There are other
people watching—
31:
You sure can talk the talk, but are
you ready to walk the walk?!
34:
Ha! More than you, I bet! You're in for
it now!
37:
So uh... Why exactly are they so mad
at each other?
48:
Thanks for sticking around! Our next
song is even more hype—
50:
You lot need to scram! You're in the
way!
54:
H-huh? But... We have permission
from the Guild to be here...
57:
Guild Shmild. I'M the one who owns
this place. You've got some guts
prancing around without MY
permission.
60:
You say that like we're supposed to
know who you are.
63:
You mean you don't? She's
Symphonia, leader of her very own
musical troupe.
65:
Running around someone's turf
without even saying hello... You need
to be taught a lesson.
67:
You can shove that lesson up yours.
We don't need your permission to be
here.
70:
*scoff* Let me tell you how things
work around here, newbie: keep up
the attitude, and I'll make sure you
never perform in Saga again!
74: What, scared that we'll show you up?
77:
As if! An arrogant nobody like you
could never hold a candle to me!
82:
Er... Everybody, take a deep breath.
We can talk this out—
85:
Oh, shut it! I'm not walking away
until we've settled this!
88: You wanna go? Then let's go!
91:
If you lose, you're banned from
performing on my turf ever again!
93:
Loser does what the winner says?
Works for me!
98:
H-huuuuh?! Are you serious?! Oh my
gosh, this isn't gonna end well!
103: Eh, let them go at it. Could be fun.
107:
Honestly, it might be easier to let
them get it out of their systems...
113: You're just going along with it?!
116:
Whoever earns the most while
busking will be declared the winner!
117:
Don't worry—even when I win, I'll
consider letting you off the hook if
you get down on your knees and
beg!
119: Well, aren't you just a saint.
122:
Snap out of it, Sakura. We've got this.
Trust me.
132: Let's get this show on the road!
137: Whoa... They've got this in the bag!
141:
...Maybe, maybe not. The
competition ain't too shabby.
144: Guess she wasn't just talk after all.
149:
Heh, that punk's pretty good.
But we won't let her hog the
spotlight. Right, Sakura?
152: Yeah! No point holding back now!
158:
Final tally's done. The winner is...
Franchouchou!
163:
That was pretty fun! You put up one
helluva fight.
166:
What is the meaning of this? Did you
properly count all the money?!
168:
I-I swear I did—but they ended up
earning just a little more than you!
170:
Then they must've slipped some
coins in while we weren't looking!
173:
Yeah? How? There were eyes on us
the whole time.
177:
We won fair and square, and you
know it.
180:
Don't think you're better than me,
just because you beat me once! I'll
show you who's boss next time!
183:
Heh, come back anytime you want
another ass kicking!
187:
Um, can we... not? We already won,
so...
190:
The battle, sure, but not the war! You
and me, we'll take her on as many
times as she wants!
199: Come on, let's go for another round.
201:
Gotta prove to the world that
Franchouchou has what it takes to
win it all!
